Class Overlay

  • java.lang.Object
    • platform.game.Actor
      • platform.game.Overlay
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Actor>

    public class Overlay
extends Actor
    Overlay prompts specific informations about the Player, also adds the possibility to change the gravity through SelectGravity
